---
import Layout from "../../layouts/layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Vibe Coding AI Content Engineer - Zabaca">
	<main class="zabaca-inspired">
		<!-- Custom Nav with Zabaca styling -->
		<nav class="zabaca-nav">
			<div class="nav-container">
				<!-- Logo -->
				<a href="/" class="logo">Zabaca</a>
				
				<!-- Center Links -->
				<div class="nav-links">
					<a href="/careers">Careers</a>
					<a href="/press">Press</a>
				</div>
				
				<!-- Right Actions -->
				<div class="nav-actions">
					<a href="/app" class="start-button">
						<span>Start for free</span>
					</a>
					<a href="/login" class="login-link">Login</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</nav>

		<!-- Job Header -->
		<section class="job-header">
			<div class="header-container">
				<a href="/careers" class="back-link">← Back to Careers</a>
				<h1>Vibe Coding AI Content Engineer</h1>
				<div class="job-meta">
					<span class="location">REMOTE</span>
					<span class="department">Content</span>
					<span class="type">Part-time (20 hours/week)</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Job Content -->
		<section class="job-content">
			<div class="content-container">
				<div class="intro-section">
					<h2>What's Vibe Coding?</h2>
					<p>Vibe coding is the art of programming through natural conversation with AI. It's about getting into flow state with Claude, GPT-4, or your AI of choice, and building amazing things together. No more syntax memorization—just pure creative problem-solving.</p>
					
					<p>We need someone who lives and breathes this new paradigm to help others discover its power.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="section">
					<h2>The Mission</h2>
					<p>Create content that helps developers transition from traditional coding to AI-assisted development. You'll produce:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>In-depth guides on vibe coding techniques</li>
						<li>Research articles on AI coding patterns</li>
						<li>Video tutorials showing real vibe coding sessions</li>
						<li>Case studies of complex projects built entirely through AI collaboration</li>
						<li>Best practices for different AI coding assistants</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="section">
					<h2>Your Vibe</h2>
					<ul>
						<li>You've built real projects using only AI conversations</li>
						<li>You can explain complex technical concepts in simple terms</li>
						<li>You're excited about the future where everyone can code</li>
						<li>You understand both the power and limitations of AI coding</li>
						<li>You love teaching and sharing knowledge</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="section">
					<h2>What You'll Actually Do</h2>
					<ul>
						<li><strong>Create Weekly Content</strong> - One major piece per week (guide, tutorial, or research)</li>
						<li><strong>Build in Public</strong> - Document your vibe coding sessions and share insights</li>
						<li><strong>Engage the Community</strong> - Respond to questions and foster discussions</li>
						<li><strong>Experiment</strong> - Try new AI tools and techniques, then teach others</li>
						<li><strong>Collaborate</strong> - Work with me to understand what content our users need most</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="section">
					<h2>Perfect Day Example</h2>
					<p>Monday morning. Coffee in hand. You open Claude and start a conversation about building a real-time collaborative editor. Four hours later, you have a working prototype and a head full of insights. You spend the afternoon turning that session into a guide that will help thousands of developers have their "aha" moment with AI coding.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="section">
					<h2>The Perks</h2>
					<ul>
						<li>$50-80k/year for 20 hours/week (based on experience)</li>
						<li>$200/month AI tools budget (on top of salary)</li>
						<li>Work from anywhere, anytime</li>
						<li>4-day work week</li>
						<li>3 months PTO (yes, really)</li>
						<li>Equity in Zabaca</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="section">
					<h2>Not Looking For</h2>
					<ul>
						<li>Traditional technical writers who haven't embraced AI</li>
						<li>SEO content farms or keyword stuffers</li>
						<li>People who think AI will replace developers (it enhances us)</li>
						<li>Perfectionists who can't ship (vibe coding is about iteration)</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="apply-section">
					<h2>Ready to Vibe?</h2>
					<p>Don't send a traditional resume. Show me something you've built with AI. Share a conversation transcript. Link to your best vibe coding content. Tell me why this role excites you.</p>
					<a href="mailto:james@zabaca.com?subject=Vibe%20Coding%20Content%20Engineer" class="apply-button">
						Start the Conversation → james@zabaca.com
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	/* Import web fonts */
	@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fredoka:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');
	
	/* Modern design base styles */
	.zabaca-inspired {
		font-family: 'Fredoka', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
		color: #131416;
		font-weight: 400;
		-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
		-moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
		background-color: white;
		min-height: 100vh;
	}

	/* Navigation (same as careers page) */
	.zabaca-nav {
		position: fixed;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		background-color: #4ff37d;
		z-index: 50;
		padding: 16px 8px;
	}
	
	.nav-container {
		max-width: 1536px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: space-between;
		padding: 0 16px;
	}
	
	.logo {
		font-size: 24px;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #131416;
		text-decoration: none;
		letter-spacing: -0.03em;
		font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif;
	}
	
	.nav-links {
		display: flex;
		gap: 32px;
		align-items: center;
	}
	
	.nav-links a {
		color: #131416;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: 16px;
		font-weight: 500;
		transition: opacity 0.2s;
	}
	
	.nav-links a:hover {
		opacity: 0.7;
	}
	
	.nav-actions {
		display: flex;
		gap: 24px;
		align-items: center;
	}
	
	.start-button {
		position: relative;
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 12px 24px;
		background-color: #131416;
		color: white;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 100px;
		font-weight: 600;
		font-size: 16px;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	
	.start-button:hover {
		transform: scale(1.05);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
	}
	
	.login-link {
		color: #131416;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: 16px;
		font-weight: 500;
		transition: opacity 0.2s;
	}
	
	.login-link:hover {
		opacity: 0.7;
	}

	/* Job Header */
	.job-header {
		background-color: #00c2ff;
		padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem 2rem;
		margin-top: 72px;
		border-bottom-left-radius: 50% 60px;
		border-bottom-right-radius: 50% 60px;
	}

	.header-container {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.back-link {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: white;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 500;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		opacity: 0.9;
	}

	.back-link:hover {
		opacity: 1;
		transform: translateX(-4px);
	}

	.job-header h1 {
		font-size: 3.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: white;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		letter-spacing: -0.03em;
		line-height: 1.1;
	}

	.job-meta {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.job-meta span {
		background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
		color: white;
		padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
		border-radius: 100px;
		font-weight: 600;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	}

	/* Job Content */
	.job-content {
		padding: 4rem 2rem 6rem 2rem;
	}

	.content-container {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.intro-section {
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		padding-bottom: 3rem;
		border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
	}

	.intro-section h2 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		color: #131416;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}

	.intro-section p {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: #131416;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.section {
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.section h2 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		color: #131416;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}

	.section p {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: #666;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.section ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
	}

	.section li {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: #666;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		padding-left: 2rem;
		position: relative;
	}

	.section li:before {
		content: "→";
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: #00c2ff;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 1.25rem;
	}

	.section li strong {
		color: #131416;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	/* Apply Section */
	.apply-section {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 3rem;
		background-color: #f8f8f8;
		border-radius: 30px;
		margin-top: 4rem;
	}

	.apply-section h2 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		color: #131416;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}

	.apply-section p {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: #666;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.apply-button {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		background-color: #131416;
		color: white;
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 100px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 600;
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.apply-button:hover {
		transform: scale(1.05);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	/* Mobile responsiveness */
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.nav-links {
			display: none;
		}

		.job-header h1 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}

		.intro-section h2 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.section h2 {
			font-size: 1.75rem;
		}
	}
</style>